	<section class="article-content clearfix" itemprop="articleBody">
				
		<p> </p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 150%;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 'Times New Roman',serif; color: blue;">About us</span></p>
<p> </p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 150%;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 'Times New Roman',serif;"><span style="color: #000000;">Young Yaa Pty Ltd is a cultural media company located in Sydney CBD. The company is dedicated to promoting appreciation for Chinese traditional culture and aims to enhance cultural communication between Australia and China by hosting different types of sport and cultural events which involve domestic and international exhibition, sports competition, concerts and team build-up activities. We have organized </span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 'Times New Roman',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体;"><span style="color: #000000;">diverse events, including three major football matches, two basketball tournaments and numerous stimulating entertainment events. Meanwhile, we are developing business in China and have made achievements in similar industry as well. The company has gained proficiency in employing marketing methods to carry forward Chinese traditional</span> <span style="color: #000000;">culture and is enthusiastic about putting more efforts and contributions in events industry. </span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 'Times New Roman',serif;"><span style="color: #000000;">Apart from daily work and study, we would love to provide people with opportunities of enjoying pleasant collective activities and meeting more like-minded friends to promote multi-culture exchange. </span></span></p>
<p> </p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 150%;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 'Times New Roman',serif;"><span style="color: #000000;"> </span></span></p>
<p> </p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 150%;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 'Times New Roman',serif; color: blue;">Why choose us</span><span lang="ZH-CN" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: blue;">？</span></p>
<p> </p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt 12pt; line-height: 150%; text-indent: -12pt; mso-char-indent-count: -1.0;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 'Times New Roman',serif;"><span style="color: #000000;">-- Experience in sports, entertainment events and traditional festivals planning</span></span></p>
<p> </p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 150%;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 'Times New Roman',serif;"><span style="color: #000000;">-- A large number of potential Asian participants</span></span></p>
<p> </p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 150%;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 'Times New Roman',serif;"><span style="color: #000000;">-- Various business opportunities in Australia and oversea</span></span></p>
<p> </p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 150%;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 'Times New Roman',serif;"><span style="color: #000000;">-- Strong language and background knowledge support e.g Volunteers</span></span></p>
<p> </p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 150%;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 'Times New Roman',serif;"><span style="color: #000000;">-- Massive existing participants</span></span></p>
<p> </p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 150%;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 'Times New Roman',serif;"><span style="color: #000000;">-- Closed cooperation with Asian companies </span></span></p>
<p> </p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 150%;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 'Times New Roman',serif;"><span style="color: #000000;"> </span></span></p>
<p> </p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 150%;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 'Times New Roman',serif;"><span style="color: #000000;">If you would like to develop business or promote events in an Asian group, it’s a potential win-win for both of us to support each other. We would like to hear from you if you are interested in any kind of cooperation. </span></span></p>
<p> </p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 150%;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 'Times New Roman',serif;"><span style="color: #000000;">Thank you! </span></span></p>
<p> </p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; text-align: left; line-height: 150%;" align="left"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 'Times New Roman',serif;"><span style="color: #000000;"> </span></span></p>
<p> </p>
